reviewText: I saw this documentary on the History Channel and wanted it to share with our group that cruised Alaska last summer.  It's a great DVD about the entire history of Alaska.

Very informative. I was part of the pipeline crew depicted in the document. I was in it for about 2 seconds, so I might be partial. It brought back some good memories of my Alaskan adventure shared by thousands who worked on the pipeline. I bet a lot of old 798 pipeline union members would like this DVD.
